1. Definitions

  "Managed Service": Providing the functionality of this 
  software to external third parties as a hosted or managed 
  service, whether or not the use of this software is 
  disclosed to end users. Internal use within an organization 
  is permitted.

  "AI Training": Using this software, its source code, 
  documentation, outputs, logs, or synthetic derivatives 
  to train, fine-tune, or distill machine learning or 
  AI models.

  "European Entity": An entity directly entering into this 
  license that is headquartered in the EEA or Switzerland, 
  provided its ultimate parent company is also located 
  within these territories. This determination is based 
  solely on the entity directly using this software, not 
  any parent, subsidiary, or affiliated entity.

  "AI Agent": An automated system generating or submitting 
  code without direct, line-by-line human review and 
  manual submission.

  "Annual Revenue": The total global revenue of the entity 
  and its ultimate parent company combined, in the most 
  recently completed fiscal year.

2. Grant of Rights

  You are granted a worldwide, royalty-free license to use, 
  copy, modify, and distribute this software and derivatives 
  for any purpose, subject to the limitations below.

3. Limitations

  (a) Managed Service: You may not provide a Managed Service 
      based on this software without a commercial license 
      from the copyright holder.

  (b) AI Training: You may not use this software for AI 
      Training without a commercial license from the 
      copyright holder. Reproduction of three or more 
      consecutive lines of this software's source code, 
      documentation, or outputs by an AI system shall 
      constitute prima facie evidence of unauthorized AI 
      Training use, subject to rebuttal by the accused party.

4. Trademark

  No rights are granted to the name "[Project Name]" or 
  associated logos or trademarks.

5. Contributions

  Contributors retain their copyright but grant the copyright 
  holder a perpetual, irrevocable, and sublicensable license 
  to use, modify, and distribute all contributions under any 
  terms.

  Contributions must be submitted by a human being acting 
  in their own capacity. Contributions submitted by or on 
  behalf of AI Agents are not accepted and will be rejected.

6. Patent Grant

  Each contributor grants you a license under their essential 
  patent claims to use and distribute this software. Any 
  party that initiates patent litigation against this 
  software automatically and immediately terminates their 
  rights under this license.

7. Enforcement, Audit & Damages

  Any breach of Section 3 automatically and immediately 
  terminates this license unless cured within the following 
  period after written notice from the copyright holder:

  (a) 90 days for entities with Annual Revenue below 
      EUR 1 million;

  (b) 30 days for entities with Annual Revenue between 
      EUR 1 million and EUR 100 million;

  (c) Termination is immediate and permanent for entities 
      with Annual Revenue exceeding EUR 100 million.

  Upon written notice specifying the alleged breach, the 
  copyright holder may demand an independent audit no more 
  than once per calendar year. The audit shall commence 
  within 10 business days of notice. If a violation is 
  found, the audited party bears all audit and legal costs.

  Damages — all entities:

    Damages shall equal the greater of:

    (a) three times a reasonable commercial royalty 
        reflecting the value of a license that would 
        have been agreed upon between the parties at 
        the time of the violation, or

    (b) the revenue attributable to the infringing use, 
        which in the absence of clear evidence to the 
        contrary shall be presumed to constitute no less 
        than 10% of the violating entity's Annual Revenue 
        during the period of violation.

    In case of AI Training violations, the period of 
    violation shall encompass the entire commercial 
    lifetime of the AI model or system trained on this 
    software.

